XBRL IFRS Accounting Taxonomy Support API for C#, .NET Apps
item.description: Aspose.Finance for .NET 22.5 Download  Support Forum  File Details Downloads: 1 File Size: 6.5 MB Date Added: : 5 days ago [5/11/2022] Release Noteshttps://releases.aspose.com/finance/net/release-notes/2022/aspose-finance-for-net-22-5-release-notes/ File Details Handle Schema from xbrl.ifrs.org Ability to handle schema from xbrl.ifrs.org (IFRS Accounting Taxonomy). Support for Nested Non-Numeric Facts The support to handle nested nonNumeric facts has been added. Support for Inline XBRL exclude Element The support has been added for the exclude element which can be used to encapsulate data that is not to be included while processing the footnote or nonNumeric elements.
